The paper discusses the use of program transformation techniques to enhance model checking, which involves verifying the correctness of a system by checking all possible executions. This topic is closely related to the areas of logic (cs.LO), programming languages (cs.PL), software engineering (cs.SE), formal languages and automata theory (cs.FL), and software engineering (cs.SC).
